# FitConnect - Social Fitness App

```mermaid

erDiagram

    User ||--o{ Friend : follows
    User ||--o{ Post : creates
    User ||--o{ Image : uploads
    User ||--o{ Comment : creates
    User ||--o{ Like : gives
    
    User {
        int User_ID PK
        string First_Name
        string Last_Name
        date DOB
        string Address
        string City
        string State
        int Zip_Code
        string Country
        int Phone
        string Email
        string Username
        string Password
    }
    
    Friend {
        int Friend_ID PK
        int User_ID FK
    }
    
    Post ||--o{ Image : contains
    Post ||--o{ Comment : contains
    Post ||--o{ Like : contains
    Post ||--o{ Tag : contains
    
    Post {
        int Post_ID PK
        int User_ID FK
        date Date
        string Text
        int Like_Count
        int Comment_Count
    }

    Image {
        int User_ID FK
        int Post_ID FK
        image Image
    }

    Comment {
        int User_ID FK
        int Post_ID FK
        string Text
    }

    Like {
        int User_ID FK
        int Post_ID FK
    }

    Tag {
        int User_ID FK
        int Post_ID FK
    }
```
